cat << EOF
Linux-VServer provides virtualization for GNU/Linux systems. This is 
accomplished by kernel level isolation. It allows to run multiple virtual units
at once. Those units are sufficiently isolated to guarantee the required 
security, but utilize available resources efficiently, as they run on the same
kernel.
EOF
